---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn more about Dan Glorioso - CS Student @ Tufts, Full-Stack Developer, and passionate technologist">
	<section id="about">
		<div class="h-full w-full flex flex-col gap-12 md:gap-16">
			
			<!-- Hero Section -->
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
				<!-- Left: Photo -->
				<div class="flex-shrink-0">
					<div class="w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-border-primary">
						<img src="/me.jpeg" alt="Dan Glorioso" class="h-full w-full object-cover"/>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<!-- Right: Intro -->
				<div class="flex-1">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">
						Hey, I'm Dan
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-secondary mb-4">
						CS Student @ Tufts • Full-Stack Developer
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg text-text-tertiary leading-relaxed">
						I'm passionate about building things that matter—whether that's elegant web applications, 
						open-source projects, or creative solutions to real-world problems. When I'm not coding, 
						you'll find me exploring new technologies, working on side projects, or diving into my hobbies.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- About Me Section -->
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">About Me</h2>
				<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8">
					<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
						<p class="text-text-tertiary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
							I'm currently pursuing my Computer Science degree at Tufts University, where I'm diving deep into 
							algorithms, systems design, and software engineering principles. What excites me most about CS is the 
							ability to turn ideas into reality—to write code that solves problems and creates value for people.
						</p>
						<p class="text-text-tertiary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
							My journey in tech started with curiosity and a desire to understand how things work. Over time, 
							that curiosity evolved into a passion for building web applications, optimizing performance, and 
							creating user experiences that feel seamless and intuitive.
						</p>
						<p class="text-text-tertiary text-lg leading-relaxed">
							I believe great software comes from understanding both the technical and human sides of development. 
							That's why I focus not just on writing clean, efficient code, but also on creating solutions that 
							are accessible, maintainable, and genuinely useful.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Interests & Hobbies Section -->
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Interests & Hobbies</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					
					<!-- Interest Card 1 -->
					<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-200">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Open Source</h3>
								<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
									I love contributing to open-source projects and building tools that help other developers. 
									There's something rewarding about code that lives beyond a single project.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Interest Card 2 -->
					<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-200">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Learning & Experimentation</h3>
								<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
									I'm always exploring new technologies, frameworks, and programming paradigms. 
									Currently diving into performance optimization, TypeScript patterns, and modern web APIs.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Interest Card 3 -->
					<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-200">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Reading & Writing</h3>
								<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
									I enjoy reading technical blogs, documentation, and books about software engineering. 
									I also write about my learnings and share them on my blog.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Interest Card 4 -->
					<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-200">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Music & Creative Projects</h3>
								<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
									I have a deep appreciation for music and enjoy working on creative projects. 
									I've built websites for musicians and love exploring the intersection of tech and art.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Interest Card 5 -->
					<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-200">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Collaboration</h3>
								<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
									I thrive in collaborative environments and enjoy working with others to solve complex problems. 
									Some of my best work comes from bouncing ideas off teammates and learning from different perspectives.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Interest Card 6 -->
					<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-border-accent transition-all duration-200">
						<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
							<div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Side Projects</h3>
								<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
									I'm always working on side projects—from web apps to developer tools. 
									These projects let me experiment with new ideas and technologies in a low-stakes environment.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- What I'm Looking For Section -->
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">What I'm Looking For</h2>
				<div class="bg-bg-card backdrop-blur-sm border border-border-primary rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8">
					<p class="text-text-tertiary text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
						I'm always open to connecting with fellow developers, potential collaborators, and opportunities 
						that align with my interests. Whether you're working on an interesting project, looking for a 
						collaborator, or just want to chat about tech, feel free to reach out!
					</p>
					<p class="text-text-tertiary text-lg leading-relaxed">
						I'm particularly interested in opportunities where I can work on meaningful problems, learn from 
						experienced engineers, and contribute to projects that have real impact. If you think we'd be a 
						good fit, I'd love to hear from you.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Contact Form -->
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Get In Touch</h2>
				<ContactForm />
			</div>

		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
